{"tid":891291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(估國家）食客打邊爐撈出死老鼠　老闆：老鼠也是糧食餵大","createTime":"2018-11-06T04:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T10:10:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4787a829bc230491269a157bc58bc33189987a9a","tid":891291,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:01:15.000Z","msg":"11月06日(二) 02:43  <br />\n更多新聞短片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n重慶渝中區有4名食客在一間連鎖火鍋店用餐，竟在湯底中撈出一隻被煮熟的死老鼠。其中一名食客表示，與老闆理論時，對方竟稱「老鼠也是糧食餵大」。據火鍋店老闆則表示，已向食藥監局和警方報警，正調查火鍋湯底出現死老鼠的原因。 <br />\n<br />\n據老闆表示，4名食客大約中午12時到火鍋店，選擇了店外的餐桌就餐，一共叫了9道火鍋配菜。老闆續稱，大概10分鐘後，食客向店員表示在湯底發現了老鼠。片段中，在九宮格的火鍋裏，一名食客用筷子從中間格子中夾起一隻老鼠，該老鼠較大，全身黝黑。 <br />\n<br />\n據食客發文聲稱，火鍋店老闆曾在事後向他們表示：「吃出了問題，再來找我們。」惟食客不接受這個說法，認為身體因此出問題，找火鍋老闆已是為時已晚。食客更表示老鼠不是自己帶去的，稱：「為了200多元人民幣（約230港元），誰還隨身帶隻老鼠。」 <br />\n<br />\n老闆表示，事發後，已第一時間向當事人表達歉意。食客在拍攝影片和拍照後離開，並未留下聯繫方式。他更回應稱，事後立即組織員工開會檢討，惟暫時仍不知老鼠從哪裏來，也不確定是哪個生產環節出問題。老闆又指，一次性的火鍋湯底都是由企業配送，使用時才拆包裝倒入鍋內。"},{"pid":"4cb6464cc584c14807c3fb31bd25ea8185001855","tid":891291,"uid":3117,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:02:35.000Z","msg":"打邊爐送老鼠仲想點"},{"pid":"e94bb028aa48134d7d95b913614f64bc162cde59","tid":891291,"uid":76105,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:04:51.000Z","msg":"唔記得起肉ja<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大驚小怪"},{"pid":"600ed0f90f8b7bb615a8367fb2a0b65e129af80e","tid":891291,"uid":15193,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:05:41.000Z","msg":"hello moto?"},{"pid":"874ffd871e3c5c7173bdf466fdfe28d23b50eaab","tid":891291,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e94bb028aa48134d7d95b913614f64bc162cde59","tid":891291,"uid":76105,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:04:51.000Z","msg":"唔記得起肉ja<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大驚小怪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:23:49.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aded4630ea56ae4c731a137507fa9fc90f7e1e5","tid":891291,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe402e884e96caa99820d6b8760ad335d1f7af36","tid":891291,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T06:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dfc012a219a3c22a6c052fc45f19661f057c94","tid":891291,"uid":53421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"874ffd871e3c5c7173bdf466fdfe28d23b50eaab","tid":891291,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e94bb028aa48134d7d95b913614f64bc162cde59","tid":891291,"uid":76105,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:04:51.000Z","msg":"唔記得起肉ja<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大驚小怪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:23:49.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T06:46:11.000Z","msg":"本身拎黎整雞煲用"},{"pid":"0f21a885c86f60608b6a596156e04a03f69506ba","tid":891291,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640ead2a0c77d90f0e63225422b487443f4f1216","tid":891291,"uid":65400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:41:40.000Z","msg":"重慶火鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520d09236c1290268830eb4f128521b16311d56b","tid":891291,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img s